  </prolog>
  <refbody>
<section id="sidebar-toc-missing">
<title>Sidebar TOC is missing</title>
<ul>
  <li>confirm <codeph>nav-toc=full</codeph> is set</li>
  <li>confirm you're building a map (not a single topic)</li>
  <li>confirm CSS is copied to output</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="chunking-no-pages">
<title>Chunking did not produce separate pages</title>
<ul>
  <li>confirm <codeph>@chunk</codeph> is set on the correct <codeph>topicref</codeph></li>
  <li>inspect preprocessed files in temp directory</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="xsl-overrides-missing">
<title>XSL overrides do not show up</title>
<ul>
  <li>confirm your plug-in is installed in the correct DITA-OT instance</li>
  <li>run <codeph>dita --install</codeph></li>
  <li>verify <codeph>plugin.xml</codeph> has <codeph>require plugin=&quot;org.dita.html5&quot;</codeph></li>
  <li>verify extension points are correct (<codeph>dita.xsl.html5</codeph>, <codeph>dita.xsl.html5.toc</codeph>)</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="external-links-not-firing">
<title>External links template doesn't fire</title>
<ul>
  <li>the final URI may not be stored in <codeph>@href</codeph></li>
  <li>locate the default link/href computation logic and override there</li>
</ul>
</section>
<section id="broke-after-upgrade">
<title>Everything broke after upgrade</title>
<ul>
  <li>re-check import paths (especially TOC)</li>
  <li>reduce overrides to minimal set</li>
  <li>prefer wrappers + next-match rather than large copied templates</li>
</ul>
</section>
  </refbody>
</reference>
